{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"93a1aae6bb","title":"李富春给全国总工会四个组织的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"362fcd0fde","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":3,"articleId":"93a1aae6bb"}],"tags":[{"id":"25e2abfb25","name":"李富春","type":"人物"},{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3df4ae75e1","name":"干部和干部政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"a59dfa2519","name":"各级党政领导人","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9c4175f9ee","name":"李富春"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0c3510e6dc","type":"title","text":"李富春给全国总工会四个组织的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"76bcf6781c","type":"paragraph","text":"中华全国总工会工人文工团、毛泽东思想红卫兵、毛泽东思想宣传队、红旗公社、中华全国总工会机关《国际红旗》公社、革命的同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"5635d6af85","type":"paragraph","text":"看了你们二月二十八日的信和“红旗”第一期，我和康生同志有下列意见向你们建议：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"dd30326617","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）刘宁一同志，中央认为不是“三反分子”。因此，你们的“红旗”第一期材料不能公开散发。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"f2f6032358","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）你们不能把马纯古等人所谓揭露刘宁一同志的材料，作为你们的材料，来揭露刘宁一。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"714d63ee4f","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）希望你们好好学习《红旗》杂志四期社论，和人民日报发表的《我们鲁迅兵团向何处去？》等重要文章，来提高政策水平。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"2ed2e883af","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）你们的报刊不要用”红旗”的名义，以免与中央的红旗杂志混淆起来。等待你们把文件学完后再找你们。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"86c40cad20","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化革命敬礼！","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"},{"id":"ca1140b201","type":"paragraph","text":"富春三月三日","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb"}],"page":{"id":"37530f05ea","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"93a1aae6bb","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}